3. **JSON Processing**: Added a sophisticated JSON extraction function that can handle both well-formed JSON and text that contains JSON-like structures

4. **Prioritization Workflow**: Modified to collect and process all 10 answers at once in a more structured format

5. **Encoding Fixes**: Added proper UTF-8 encoding for all file operations to handle Arabic text

6. **Fallback Mechanisms**: Added fallback options when processes fail (e.g., default questions, structured document creation)

